  "faq": {
    "titulo": "Frequently Asked Questions",
    "q1": "Is ZenyFin free?",
    "a1": "Yes! We offer a complete free plan with essential features for personal financial control. As your needs grow, you can upgrade to a paid plan.",
    "q2": "Is my data safe?",
    "a2": "Absolutely. We use end-to-end encryption and strictly follow LGPD to protect your information.",
    "q3": "Can I use it on my phone?",
    "a3": "Yes! ZenyFin is fully responsive and works perfectly on any device.",
    "q4": "How does the multi-user plan work?",
    "a4": "On Pro and Enterprise plans, you can invite members to share financial control with different permission levels.",
    "q5": "Can I cancel anytime?",
    "a5": "Yes! You can cancel your subscription at any time with no fees. Your access continues until the end of the paid period."
  },
